title: New player on Oceania needs help with competitive
body:
HI! I'm an old professional player on my country on EUW (spain) and i want to move to OCE because of my gf.
I would apreciate if u help me with top teams like i dont know nothing about league in your country, thanks mates.
My acc name is: Hi im not Vayne

replies.body: If you are talented enough to be notice in the challenger solo Q scene, then am sure some team would want to pick to up. However if you are not, i doubt any professional team will.

There are professional teams, or what we consider to be the best.
4 top as far as I know are Chiefs, Dire Wolves, Immunity and Legacy.
But we have no teams that play in worlds or anything like that.

Pretty Much non-existent
As for worlds, I find a lot of people support TSM
This is my main, in Oce dont exist professional teams?
